 (1989-1991); Teacher, Namibia, (1977-1988) and Teacher, SA, (1976).<\/p>\n<p>Career2:<\/p>\n<p>Member of the Swapo Party Central Committee since 2012; Member of the National Executive Committee for the SPWC since 2012; Member of the Central Committee of SPWC since 2011; Khorixas District Coordinator SPWC (2006-2014); Branch Coordinator for the Swapo Party Women\u2019s Council for the Maxwilili Branch in Khorixas (2004-2006); Member of the Local Authority Council, (1992-2003)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Legislative Interests<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\u00a0Human Resources; Community Development; Foreign Affairs; Social Development and education.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Deputy Minister: Gender Equality, Poverty Eradication &amp; Child Welfare SWAPO Party Legislative Profile Member of the National Assembly (2015-2020); Deputy Minister of Environment and Tourism since February 2018. Personal Born on 26 February 1958, Reimvasmaak, South Africa Education Bachelor of Philosophy in Education, University of Exeter , UK (2002); Post Graduate Diploma in English Language&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2420,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","dt_team_category":[104,92],"class_list":["post-2419","dt_team","type-dt_team","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","dt_team_category-6th-national-assembly-2015-2020","dt_team_category-7th-national-assembly-2020-2025","dt_team_category-104","dt_team_category-92","description-off"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_team\/2419","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_team"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/dt_team"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2419"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.